{"tha-ap469:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap469:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap469:0.3":"7 Labujaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap469:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap469:1.2":"aramiko aham tada; ","tha-ap469:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap469:1.4":"gacchantam anilanjase. ","tha-ap469:2.1":"Labujam phalamadaya, ","tha-ap469:2.2":"buddhasetthassadasaham; ","tha-ap469:2.3":"Akaseva thito santo, ","tha-ap469:2.4":"patigganhi mahayaso. ","tha-ap469:3.1":"Vittisanjanano mayham, ","tha-ap469:3.2":"ditthadhammasukhavaho; ","tha-ap469:3.3":"Phalam buddhassa datvana, ","tha-ap469:3.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap469:4.1":"Adhiganchim tada pitim, ","tha-ap469:4.2":"vipulam sukhamuttamam; ","tha-ap469:4.3":"Uppajjateva ratanam, ","tha-ap469:4.4":"nibbattassa tahim tahim. ","tha-ap469:5.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap469:5.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap469:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap469:5.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap469:6.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap469:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap469:6.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap469:7.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap469:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap469:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap469:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap469:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap469:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap469:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma labujaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap469:10.1":"Labujaphaladayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}